Valet parking
* Valet parking, fee: 66 USD daily

Electric car charging stations
* Complimentary 

Subway Station
* Powell Street BART Station

Airport
* San Francisco International Airport (SFO)
* Super Shuttle - (415) 558-8500 / supershuttle.com; fee: 17 USD (one way) ;reservation required;;Estimated taxi fare: 40 USD (one way);Take US-101 N. Slight right onto I-80 E (signs for Bay Bridge/Oakland). Take exit 1A toward US-101 N. Merge onto 7th St. Turn right onto Folsom St. Turn left onto 6th St. Continue onto Golden Gate Ave/Taylor St. Turn right onto Taylor St. Turn right onto Post St. Destination will be on the left.
* Oakland International Airport (OAK)
* Super Shuttle - (415) 558-8500 / supershuttle.com; fee: 27 USD (one way) ;reservation required; PHONE: 1 510-563-3300;Estimated taxi fare: 60 USD (one way);Merge onto I-880 N via the ramp to Downtown/Oakland. Take exit 46A on the left for I-80 W toward San Francisco/Bay Bridge. Keep left at the fork and merge onto I-80 W. Take exit 2C to merge onto Fremont St. Turn left onto Mission St. Turn right onto 3rd St. Turn left onto Geary St. Turn right onto Taylor St. Take the 2nd right onto Post St. Destination will be on the left.

Parking
* Valet parking ONLY USD 66 plus 14 percent tax per night - SUVs and oversized vehicles USD 76 plus tax
